Field.Text:
This report lists customers grouped by country. The map field in the group header shows customers as well as suppliers in the current country. This is achieved with 3 map layers:

- a KML layer that uses the world map KML file with ItemVisibleExpr set to "kmlItemVisible=Country" (so that only the outline of the current country shows) and auto zoom/center set to true so that the map zooms in to the current country;

- a points layer with MapLocation set to "City;Country" - this produces customers' locations on the map;

- finally, another points layer with the same MapLocation - BUT, the RecordSource for that layer is set in the group's OnFormat script to list all suppliers for the current country, which produces locations of all suppliers in the current country on the map.
